Place integration logos here.

Supported formats: SVG (preferred), PNG, or WebP.
Recommended size: 48x48 or 64x64 px with transparent background.

Files:
  google.svg   – Google (Tasks, Calendar, Gmail)
  notion.svg   – Notion (Databases, Tasks)
  jira.svg     – Jira (Issues, Projects)
  canvas.svg   – Canvas LMS (Assignments, Courses)
